"3 1/2 pounds pork baby back ribs, racks cut in half","1  (11.5-ounce) can frozen orange-pineapple-apple juice concentrate, thawed and undiluted (we tested with Welch's)","3/4 cup soy sauce","1/4 cup creamy peanut butter","1/4 cup minced fresh cilantro","2 tablespoons minced fresh ginger","1  garlic clove, pressed","2 teaspoons sugar","  Garnish: fresh cilantro sprigs"